						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone built into the wall of the temple of Basavaṇṇa.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription of about the <hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.,</hi> states that when <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēs11vara</hi> <hi rend="bold">Kīrtidēvarasa</hi> attacked the <hi rend="italic">agrahāra</hi> <hi rend="bold">Deyvada-Posavūr,</hi> a goldsmith named <hi rend="bold">Dāsōja</hi> fought with him and died.</p>						

						</summary>
